„ ===================================
„ Day 5: If You Give A Seed A Fertilizer
„ Map seeds through chain: seed->soil->fertilizer->water->light->temp->humidity->location
„ Example seeds: 79 14 55 13
„ Maps: each [dst_start src_start len] triple
„ Expected lowest location: 35
„ ===================================

„ Map lookup function: given value and map array, return mapped value
„ map array format: [dst1 src1 len1 dst2 src2 len2 ... 0]
„ Returns value if not in any range, else mapped value
d5_lookup{val;map}:
{
  resultŻval
  iŻ0
  mlenŻő map
  while (i<mlen) {
    dstŻmap[i]
    srcŻmap[i+1]
    lenŻmap[i+2]
    if ((val>=src) & (val<(src+len))) {
      resultŻval-src+dst
    }
    iŻi+3
  }
  result
}

