„ Day 8: Haunted Wasteland - Part 1
„ Follow L/R instructions on node network from AAA to ZZZ.
„ Example: RL instructions, 7 nodes. Expected steps: 2
„ ===================================

„ Instructions: R=1, L=0
d8_instŻ1 0

„ Node names encoded as 3-char arrays (A=0, B=1, ..., Z=25)
„ Node map: node_index -> (left_index, right_index)
„ AAA=0, BBB=1, CCC=2, DDD=3, EEE=4, GGG=5, ZZZ=6

„ AAA->BBB(1) CCC(2); BBB->DDD(3) EEE(4); CCC->ZZZ(6) GGG(5)
„ DDD->DDD(3) DDD(3); EEE->EEE(4) EEE(4); GGG->GGG(5) GGG(5); ZZZ->ZZZ(6) ZZZ(6)
d8_leftŻ1 3 6 3 4 5 6
d8_rightŻ2 4 5 3 4 5 6

d8_curŻ0       „ Start at AAA (index 0)
d8_stepsŻ0
d8_ilenŻő d8_inst
d8_foundŻ0

while (d8_found=0) {
  d8_dirŻd8_inst[d8_steps-(d8_stepsŖd8_ilen)Ŗd8_ilen]
  if (d8_dir=0) { d8_curŻd8_left[d8_cur] }
  if (d8_dir=1) { d8_curŻd8_right[d8_cur] }
  d8_stepsŻd8_steps+1
